---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Words Containing MA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy"
  description="Complete list of Scrabble words containing MA with scores, definitions, and strategic tips. Master MA words for better Scrabble plays."
  keywords="scrabble words containing ma, ma words scrabble, words with ma, scrabble ma word list, ma scrabble strategy"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Containing MA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy",
    "description": "Complete list of Scrabble words containing MA with scores, definitions, and strategic tips.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-15",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-containing-ma" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring MA words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Top MA words include MAXIMIZE (28 pts), MARZIPAN (21 pts), PHARMACY (20 pts), MAMMOTH (16 pts), and MAGICAL (12 pts). MA is one of the most common pairs with 800+ valid words." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many Scrabble words contain MA?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Over 800 valid Scrabble words contain MA. Common examples include MAKE, MATCH, HUMAN, SMALL, FORMAT, WOMAN, DRAMA, and MATERIAL." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What strategy works best with MA tiles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "MA is among the most versatile pairs in Scrabble with 800+ words. It works at the start (MAKE, MATCH, MAP), in the middle (HUMAN, SMALL, FORMAT), and at the end (DRAMA, COMMA, ENIGMA). The sheer volume means you almost always have a play available. MAXIMIZE (28 pts) is the ultimate MA target." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Letter Pair Content</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Containing MA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>4 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">MA is one of the most common letter pairs in the English language, appearing in over 800 valid Scrabble words. From everyday plays like MAKE and MATCH to premium targets like MAXIMIZE (28 pts) and PHARMACY (20 pts), MA provides endless scoring opportunities. Its flexibility at any word position makes it a cornerstone pair for competitive play.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top MA Words by Score</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MAXIMIZE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">28</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To make as large as possible</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MARZIPAN</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">21</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Almond confection</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">PHARMACY</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">20</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A dispensary</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MAMMOTH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Extremely large</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MAGICAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Having supernatural power</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MATCH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To pair or equal</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MATERIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Physical substance</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">HUMAN</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A person</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MAKE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To create</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">DRAMA</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A theatrical play</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SMALL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Little in size</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">800+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid MA words</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">13 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Average score</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Very Common</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pair frequency</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for MA Words</h2>

      <p>MA works at every position — start (MAKE, MATCH, MAP), middle (HUMAN, SMALL, FORMAT), and end (DRAMA, COMMA, ENIGMA). This flexibility means you rarely get stuck with these tiles. Focus on high-value consonants paired with MA for premium scoring: MAXIMIZE uses the X and Z tiles brilliantly. The -MATIC and -MATION suffixes extend shorter words into bingo territory.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MAXIMIZE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">28 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MARZIPAN</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">PHARMACY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MAMMOTH</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">16 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MATCH</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MAGICAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">MA provides <span class="text-white font-medium">800+ valid words</span> making it one of the most prolific pairs in Scrabble. MAXIMIZE (28 pts) is the crown jewel. MATCH (12 pts) and HUMAN (10 pts) are dependable everyday plays that work on almost any board.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/words-containing-qu" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words Containing QU — Essential Scrabble Q Words</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/words-with-multiple-vowels" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words With Multiple Vowels — Scrabble Vowel Dumps</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/four-letter-words-every-player-should-know" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Four-Letter Words Every Scrabble Player Should Know</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every MA word from your tiles — instant results, no signup</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
